{"tid":2400046,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓網「模擬演唱會減肥法」唱跳3小時　BTS粉絲實測：一個月瘦10KG","createTime":"2021-02-08T15:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T23:24:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"44abec5cb9b0e086e4f6fe5b485f9684db8f6556","tid":2400046,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:06:09.000Z","msg":"年節即將到來，擔心過年期間不小心吃太多，或許可以試試南韓粉絲的減肥法。一名防彈少年團（BTS）的粉絲分享自己的「模擬演唱會」減肥法，簡單來說就是把自己想像成歌手，開一整場演唱會。在實測一個月後，效果超級驚人。<br />\n<br />\n該名粉絲表示，要先將自己想像為成員，最好是一個Rap Line和一個Vocal Line，以她自己為例的話，選擇的對象是SUGA跟柾國。接著在播放清單準備好一整場演唱會的歌曲，接著就是從頭到尾全部跟著跳一遍。<br />\n<br />\n由於是模擬演唱會，因此在整場3小時間，可以和成員們一樣可以喝水，但不能中途停下來喘氣超過10秒。就算是沒有舞蹈的歌曲，也要一起跟著唱出來，而在原本VCR或是成員的SOLO時間中，也要假裝在換裝，不可以就這樣停下來休息。<br />\n<br />\n此外在「演唱會」的兩個小時前，就得停止進食，一切比照真實演唱會成員的情況辦理。原PO還表示：「像柾國一樣，從演唱會的前一晚，晚餐就只能吃兩根香蕉。」<br />\n<br />\n甚至在結尾時，還要像成員一樣感言講到哭出來。而歌手在舉辦巡迴時，幾乎每個月甚至每個禮拜都有演出，按照如此頻率實行後，這名粉絲表示，「在一個月內瘦了10公斤。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5447/5447978.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5447%2F5447978.gif&h=999ccb7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團《Dionysus》舞蹈。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文章最初發表在instiz，被轉發到論壇The Qoo後也引起話題，不少人說：「我曾經跟著YouTube想學BTS的舞蹈，但3分鐘後就覺得肌肉快死掉。」、「想到《Dionysus》跟《Not Today》，我已經要暈倒。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5447/5447977.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5447%2F5447977.gif&h=40bcd9d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼防彈少年團《Not Today》舞蹈。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n也有人表示，難怪先前在演唱會紀錄片中，柾國得在後台吸氧氣，「光想到這疲累程度就投降了。」更有人說：「SUGA曾經說在巡迴期間都不會刻意控制飲食和體重，因為需要很多體力，看來熱量消耗真的很大。」"},{"pid":"1612a8b3e793713420ffd2ea0995d1ace2335c9a","tid":2400046,"uid":253373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"問題係要識跳BTS d 舞先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0df6e3c7d3d39ed09fe6cfdd6194d426121de93","tid":2400046,"uid":83102,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"1612a8b3e793713420ffd2ea0995d1ace2335c9a","tid":2400046,"uid":253373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"問題係要識跳BTS d 舞先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:10:51.000Z","msg":"盡跟動作都已經係有氧運動<br />\n需然冇追開韓星<br />\n但呢點的確幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢計溜左人地假唱開"},{"pid":"c9484ca0800133aa65d8fb5d65c4f84e5b0223b6","tid":2400046,"uid":67294,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:17:35.000Z","msg":"邊睇邊笑, 韓狗真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00b2b25eca551ef92278c1a2efeb4d5265adc90","tid":2400046,"uid":28831,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:19:50.000Z","msg":"「像柾國一樣，從演唱會的前一晚，晚餐就只能吃兩根香蕉。」<br />\n晚晚剩係食兩條蕉都肥既應該拎去做燃料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bb24c5e96a70766aae2996db3d6e9518d7e200","tid":2400046,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T17:04:16.000Z","msg":"呢個新年試試先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c9882d1b020bec3055cae13599303124a3e4a6","tid":2400046,"uid":119792,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T17:30:50.000Z","msg":"甚至在結尾時，還要像成員一樣感言講到哭出來。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae115cbb679ad24e413fcdd1bdbf4ac7d23e63c7","tid":2400046,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:12:55.000Z","msg":"On99 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50aa8ab2e1de4e1bca1471dac54fa7d41f0a2539","tid":2400046,"uid":4719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:24:22.000Z","msg":"同玩三個鐘just dance差不多效果"}]}